  },
  {
    title: 'Advertising and analytics choices',
    body: 'If advertising or analytics tools are used, those providers may offer opt-out settings. Review the settings in your browser and any available account or consent controls.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Account and contact requests',
    body: 'If an account area or support contact is available, use it to request access, correction, or deletion of personal information where applicable law provides those rights.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Regional privacy rights',
    body: 'Privacy rights vary by region. Depending on where you live, you may have rights to know, access, correct, delete, or opt out of certain data uses.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Important note',
    body: 'This page provides general privacy-choice information for the website and should be reviewed by a qualified privacy professional before production use.',
  },
